            <p class="comment-content">男性观察女性，女性注意自己被别人观察。女性自身的观察者是男性，而被观察者是女性。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="438412283">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-438412283" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-438412283" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="438412283">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Thomas.Xie/">蝉</a>
                    <span>2013-11-23</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">: 	
J0-02/2249</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

